---
id: anti-overconfidence
description: Prevent overstated claims in docs and user-facing text without citations
severity: error
globs:
  - "docs/**/*.md"
  - "**/*.md"
  - "**/*.rst"
patterns:
  - name: high-confidence-words
    regex: "(?i)\b(obviously|proven|guaranteed|always|never|certainly|undoubtedly|without question)\b(?![^\[]*\])"
---

This file declares simple front-matter used by the orchestrator. The body is ignored.

